:markdown
  The ``form`` block provides structural elements for a form.

  Use them as follows:

  - ``.form``
    - ``.form__group``
      - ``.form__group__label``
        - Label text
      - ``.form__group__control``
        - Form control

:sample
  .l-container
    .form
      .form__group
        label.form__group__label Foo
        .form__group__control
          input.control.control--input(type='text')
      .form__group
        label.form__group__label bar
        .form__group__control
          input.control.control--input(type='text')
      .form__group
        .form__group__control.form__group__control--fullwidth
          label.checkbox(data-checkbox)
            input.checkbox__checkbox(type='checkbox')
            .checkbox__label
              .checkbox__label__text
                span Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consetetur elitr,
                a  Nutzungsbedingungen
                span nonumy eirmod tempor invidunt.


